title: Trapped in the Academy's Eroge
description: I woke up in the world of the eroge ‘Seka’ after writing a bad review… The God of the game ‘Seka’ said that they will kill me if I don’t get the harem ending of all 6 heroines! Such a stingy god… All right. I will try to seduce all six of them and survive until the harem endings…!
author: CandyFlower, Feelition
